title: New Girl - Complete Season 2 S02 - 720p - x265
description:
As for the season 1 (https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/15637341) don't expect the full quality of beautiful HD but rather "better than SD for half the size".

Converted from https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/13852767/New_Girl_S02_Season_2_Complete_1080p_WEB-DL_[MIXED] and let's be honest, this release was a mess.

So, I converted the audio to AAC 2.0 when it wasn't available or took it from the release when it was. Removed those AWEFUL pre and post-roll F0x ads on each episodes, resynced the subtitles to match (so, the subtitles in the wild won't work, probably).

Anyway, as always, don't hesitate to give me any suggestion.
I will (probably) do the other seasons in the coming weeks.
